- **Open Source Projects**: Incorporating the work into non-profit, open-source projects
- **Academic Research**: Using the material for research, thesis work, or academic publications
- **Non-Profit Organizations**: Using the work for registered non-profit or charitable organizations (with proper attribution)
- **Personal Blogs/Portfolios**: Showcasing the work on personal websites or portfolios to demonstrate your skills
- **Experimentation**: Modifying and testing the work for learning and skill development
