### ‚ùå PROHIBITED COMMERCIAL USE

You are **NOT allowed** to use this work for:

- **Direct Sales**: Selling the design, code, or any derivative works in any form (digital or physical)
- **Paid Products/Services**: Incorporating the work into products or services that generate revenue
- **Client Work**: Using the work in projects for paying clients or commercial contracts
- **Advertising/Marketing**: Using the work in commercial advertising, promotional materials, or marketing campaigns
- **Monetized Platforms**: Distributing the work through paid platforms, subscription services, or marketplaces (e.g., theme marketplaces, template stores, stock websites)
- **SaaS Applications**: Using the work as part of Software-as-a-Service offerings or paid web applications
- **Commercial Training**: Using the work in paid courses, workshops, or training programs
- **Fundraising**: Using the work for commercial fundraising activities (non-profit fundraising may be permitted with written approval)
- **Indirect Monetization**: Using the work on platforms where you receive ad revenue, sponsorships, or other indirect compensation
- **White-Label Products**: Rebranding and reselling the work under a different name
- **Premium Features**: Using the work as a basis for premium or paid features in any application

